{"tid":918942,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"被老婆打完好心灰意冷","createTime":"2018-11-27T15:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T18:11:56.000Z","uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5764fab7cb9bd831b12ed50962c239440dce07","tid":918942,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"老婆每個星期嗌離婚，上個星期出手打我，打我個時個表情態度，令到我好心淡，即使而家佢話以後唔會再發脾氣，我都係提唔起勁再愛佢。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打有同樣經歷<br />\n<br />\n*上兩星期，老婆無喇喇唔爽吊晒鬼，話感覺一路用佢既錢（佢感覺上90%家庭支出佢出既）。<br />\n<br />\n最後查明大家戶口既結餘，証實大家付出50/50。於是佢發唔到圍就繼續冷戰。第朝起身無啦啦郁手打我，邊打邊叫我去死廢物。打完仲話：我發洩完啦，無事你坐返過黎啦。我硬係無理佢，狗咩話打就打，話抱就抱"},{"pid":"87ff9265a8d16d19890381e3adeb607ecd3cd023","tid":918942,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"我老婆一路打一路嗌：還手啦，同你打好悶呀，唔還手，你點解唔去死"},{"pid":"a27d5aeef35d4b3c795ed1bf6737724be1149cb8","tid":918942,"uid":210990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"難分真與假"},{"pid":"038524b32951bfb44a63ae0ba58a61150d37a439","tid":918942,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:40:12.000Z","msg":"我鍾意比女人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb73e836a061f74d63ab61fc7deec0ddf22e25f","tid":918942,"uid":26380,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:41:09.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"f9bee2fcbc40a88ae48071cbbc879ba135c80fb0","tid":918942,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:41:23.000Z","msg":"你老婆幾好砌，係惡死d"},{"pid":"72cfaebaa2ba489e925770a02f9a2baeb0a3ff41","tid":918942,"uid":17606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"su變左性咩？"},{"pid":"a266af5e9b5724863be81d41ad4636ff7521e0ce","tid":918942,"uid":70195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"老婆要簡金盈果種"},{"pid":"df9bc689760f91171a3a4328049b2bfdf3ccbb62","tid":918942,"uid"